{"tid":1423148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察與路西法效應","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:42:14.000Z","uid":254652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"712705033162dc98f7dc218c89d361261b68a17f","tid":1423148,"uid":254652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:00:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oMX22Q3ILOk&amp;t=687s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoMX22Q3ILOk%26t%3D687s&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2BvyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=7b269d47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oMX22Q3ILOk&amp;t=687s</a> <br />\nSORRY係蝗字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiVwdBG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiVwdBG.png&h=0efda3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3xFRp6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3xFRp6.png&h=eb87b007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無意中睇到依段關於路西法效應既電影簡介,<br />\n<br />\n發現路西法效應正正發生係現今香港當中,<br />\n<br />\n路西法效應既過程<br />\n1.首先，在有意或不經意之情形下跨越自己的道德底線。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">teargas放題,對方被制服依然亂棍嘔打,警黑合作,醫院徹離站崗,推打記者, 多到數唔哂</span><br />\n2.將其他人或個體去人性化。<br />\n3.將自己去識別化。(透過匿名、變裝等方式、如：三K黨)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑衫=暴徒 藍衫白衫=自己友支持自己</span><br />\n4.分散與推諉個人之責任。(如：納粹)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上環有示威,元朗無人好合理,咁都講得出DLLM</span><br />\n5.盲目服從於權威。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幫政府,幫鄉黑鍚春袋, 現場指揮官叫你射就射,扑就扑,前線=性奴</span><br />\n6.不經批判地盲目服從團體規範。<br />\n<br />\n7.藉由不作為與冷漠，被動地容忍惡存在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察濫權越來越多,越來越明目張膽,無視法例,<br />\n<br />\n每當市民只是以言語上反抗,就會用所謂正當合適既武力去打壓,不講道理,每口歪理都有,<br />\n<br />\n依種情況出現既原因正正係路西法效應,警察擁有權力,但係無人可以監督到警察,<br />\n<br />\n所謂警監會,警察投訴科跟本形同虛設,警察更加無NUMBER,唔出示委任證,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你在沒有監督的情況下,賦予人們權力,那就是在給濫用權力通行証</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9ad654036f37c0e80529f50a735a9d30569e9ef3","tid":1423148,"uid":254652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"死魔警"},{"pid":"1bb0d22bc0ed7e0127bbb46af06f74f7e75d7f6b","tid":1423148,"uid":254652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"死魔警"},{"pid":"0e451683e560c686b79d3ed5e0c3a62ac2f0ab9a","tid":1423148,"uid":254652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"黑社會"},{"pid":"4cb8048cd339b097a97f61d55946268ee82b15b9","tid":1423148,"uid":254652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"黑社會"},{"pid":"f539558773daf643b068dcf86337e091b245c4a0","tid":1423148,"uid":254652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"push"}]}